1034
01:17:49,716 --> 01:17:50,367
Yes.

1035
01:17:50,367 --> 01:17:53,289
Did the question of Mr. Kringle's
authenticity arise at any time

1036
01:17:53,289 --> 01:17:56,034
Before or after your children met him?

1037
01:17:56,034 --> 01:17:58,416
