1082
01:21:22,974 --> 01:21:24,632
She's good. She's good.

1083
01:21:24,632 --> 01:21:27,585
I think she...misses you.

1084
01:21:30,937 --> 01:21:32,718
Tell her I said hello.

1085
01:21:37,954 --> 01:21:39,331
Bye.

1086
01:21:49,268 --> 01:21:51,002
Oh, indeed, there was.

