1224
01:33:00,025 --> 01:33:01,948
Thank you very much, young lady.

1225
01:33:01,948 --> 01:33:03,808
You're entirely welcome.

1226
01:33:03,808 --> 01:33:08,349
And, uh...Merry christmas.

1227
01:33:08,349 --> 01:33:10,276
